entries.journal_entry_description: The Alliance needs to secure any remains of the Imperial research in Restuss. The Imperial Army has brought in some of their most skilled soldiers, Urban Assault Dark Troopers. Your task is to quell this high threat by eliminating 5 of them.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You have been tasked with defeating 5 Urban Assault Dark Troopers in Restuss.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You've defeated 5 Dark Troopers and should return to Captain Redders.
